## Supporting Types

These are the value types that flow between services. They carry no behavior.

```scala
// A single document ready for indexing, produced upstream by the SQS consumer
case class WikiEditDocument(/* fields TBD */)

// A lightweight command published to SQS after each commit.
// Carries no index metadata â€” the recipient inspects current on-disk state directly.
case class CommitEvent(committedAt: Instant)
```

